OL,3,CCheshire chief constable criticises
OL,4,Ccost-cutting CCTV room closure plan
OL,6,FBut the Chief Constable says the
OL,7,Fcontrol room staff's interventions led
OL,8,Fto 600 arrests in 2025, including for
OL,9,Fserious offences such as sexual
OL,10,Fassaults, assaults, and possession of
OL,11,Fweapons.
OL,13,FThe Council is facing a #179m gap in
OL,14,Fits budget over the next four years
OL,15,Fand has been given permission by the
OL,16,Fgovernment to increase council tax by
OL,17,Fup to 7.5%.
