OL,3,CCheshire chief constable criticises
OL,4,Ccost-cutting CCTV room closure plan
OL,6,FThe authority was due to discuss its
OL,7,Fbudget at a cabinet meeting on 18
OL,8,FFebruary ahead of the final decision
OL,9,Fbeing made on 2 March.
OL,11,FMr Roberts said he decided to issue
OL,12,Fthe public statement online on the day
OL,13,Fbefore the meeting as the force "have
OL,14,Fbeen unable to have any constructive
OL,15,Fdiscussion with the council."
