OL,3,CCheshire chief constable criticises
OL,4,Ccost-cutting CCTV room closure plan
OL,6,FHe added: "I have personally made
OL,7,Fmultiple attempts to contact them to
OL,8,Fdiscuss their proposals, but have yet
OL,9,Fto receive a response, which is why I
OL,10,Ffeel my only option is to speak out to
OL,11,Flocal residents, councillors and MPs,
OL,12,Fdirectly."
OL,14,FThe council's budget savings plan said
OL,15,Fit was the responsibility of the
OL,16,Fpolice to ensure the safety of
OL,17,Fresidents not the council, but Mr
OL,18,FRoberts said: "community safety is not
OL,19,Fsolely the responsibility of the
OL,20,Fpolice".
