OL,6,FThe Chief Constable finished by
OL,7,Fsaying: "I want to make it clear that
OL,8,Fif the council goes ahead with the
OL,9,Fproposals to move to a passive,
OL,10,Funmonitored system, I have no doubt
OL,11,Fthat it will substantially diminish
OL,12,Fthe number of arrests and is likely to
OL,13,Fresult in an increase in crime levels
