OL,3,CCheshire chief constable criticises
OL,4,Ccost-cutting CCTV room closure plan
OL,6,F"Cheshire Constabulary remains
OL,7,Fcommitted to working collaboratively
OL,8,Fwith Warrington Borough Council to
OL,9,Fkeep residents safe, however I truly
OL,10,Ffeel that the proposal as currently
OL,11,Fstated is a significant backwards
OL,12,Fstep, which will have a substantial
OL,13,Fimpact on the safety and security of
OL,14,Flocal residents and businesses."
OL,16,FThe CCTV closure is just one of the
OL,17,Fhuge list of cost-cutting proposals
OL,18,Fwhich total savings of almost #40
OL,19,Fmillion.
